locale.text: This is a fire extinguisher box. Do you want to check it?
The fire extinguisher is missing! You can call the security manager to put a new one here.
There is a fire extinguisher in the box.
This is a public telephone. Who do you want to call?
I found the fire extinguisher is missing. Could you bring us a new one?
What are these boxes doing here?
These are signages to warn people from using the lift during the fire drill.
I should prepared them and place them at the right place.
Hi, how may I help you? \n
I would like to take up a loan.
What type of loan are you looking for, sir?
I am looking for a housing loan.
That is exactly what I am looking for. I will take up that loan.
That sounds quite close to what I am looking for.. do you have other type of loans available?
Thanks, but that is not what I am looking for.
Kindly follow me to my desk to fill up the application for the loan.
